{"tid":976500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又一國！5G網路設備升級 挪威也考慮封殺華為","createTime":"2019-01-10T12:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T12:25:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c91ae4a11f4801ed8036a024065ee93087081c49","tid":976500,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php4LKykb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php4LKykb.jpg&h=385a288c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國、澳洲、日本、紐西蘭和英國等國先後不准中國電信設備業者華為（Huawei）參與5G網路建設，挪威政府也在週三（9日）表示，正在考慮是否同樣封殺華為。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，由國家控股的「挪威電信」（Telenor）和競爭對手Telia，目前使用華為生產的4G設備，並正在實驗性5G網路中測試華為的設備。但在電信設備升級之前，挪威政府正在討論各項措施，以降低電信行業潛在危險。<br />\n<br />\n挪威司法部長瓦拉（Tor Mikkel Wara）表示，挪威與美國和英國等國家有同樣的擔心，擔憂在網路中發生損害國家及個人的間諜行為，「這個問題有很高的優先性...我希望在建設下一代電信網路之前就把這個問題解決掉」。<br />\n<br />\n在被問及是否會專門針對華為採取行動時，瓦拉表示，「是的，我們正在考慮其它國家已採取的措施，美國和英國已採取措施是考慮的一部分」。<br />\n<br />\n華為的挪威分公司表示，願意對華為設備進行詳細的檢測與核查，證明可以用作挪威5G網路中的安全產品。<br />\n<br />\n挪威電信在歐亞8國擁有1.73億用戶，2009年與華為簽署一份重要合約，這筆交易也成為華為全球擴張的助力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2668061\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2668061&d=2vGsy5MtbSv2V1qJzQ8czEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=94494e62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2668061&h=3be89ece\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2668061</a>"},{"pid":"b24988ba89dedf068519f0a09452aab9f1a8c1fc","tid":976500,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:23:42.000Z","msg":"強國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a6b29f0838c6f0b32cc4f588a4cd8b312a994a","tid":976500,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:24:46.000Z","msg":"幾多國聯軍"},{"pid":"ebd483cdc79fcfa98c8903cec292d97c28f668c4","tid":976500,"uid":137480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74a6b29f0838c6f0b32cc4f588a4cd8b312a994a","tid":976500,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:24:46.000Z","msg":"幾多國聯軍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:25:43.000Z","msg":"任你幾多聯軍都不夠我葉問一打一百<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}